 is observed to be\nsimilar to or higher than lower redshift LFs even if attenuated by neutral\nhydrogen. (2) All/most of the z=7.7 candidates are not LAEs. This supports the\ndecline of LF from z ~ 6 to 7.7 and reionization at z ~ 6-7.7.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Apr 2012 02:51:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
