en signal-to-interference ratio threshold and\nattenuation coefficient approach the extreme values and discuss how fading\nimpacts the performance of all schemes we evaluate in this article.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Apr 2012 11:08:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2012 10:42:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 1 Aug 2012 18:32:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-02"}
